# Frontend Components and Pages

- Use functional components and keep props typed explicitly (no implicit `any` props).
- `src/pages/*`: orchestrate data flow and layout; avoid embedding large reusable UI logic here.
- `src/components/*`: focus on reusable UI blocks; avoid direct API calls when data can come from slices/hooks.
- Keep render logic readable: extract repeated JSX into small components.
- Guard interactive states (`disabled`, `aria-*`, loading labels) on actionable UI.
- Prefer existing shared primitives (`Button`, `Input`, `Modal`, etc.) before creating new variants.
